'''藍江'''（[[寮語|寮語]]拉丁拼寫：Nam Khan，{{lang-vi|Sông Cả/瀧哿}}、{{lang|vi|Sông Lam/瀧藍}}），是[[東南亞|東南亞]]的一條河流。它發源於[[寮國|寮國]]東北部山區，流經寮國[[川壙省|川壙省]]，以及[[越南|越南]][[乂安省|乂安省]]、[[河靜省|河靜省]]，最終在越南[[北中部|北中部]]地區注入[[北部灣|北部灣]]。幹流河長512公里，<ref>Marine research in Indonesia: Issues 16-20 - Page 229 Lembaga Oceanology Nasional (Indonesia), Lembaga Ilmu Pengetahuan Indonesia - 1976 "The Ca River is the longest river in the central part of Vietnam, the main length belongs to Nghệ An and Hà Tĩnh provinces. This river possesses abundant natural resources and habitats of many valuable plants and animals,"</ref>越南境內約300公里。<ref>Journal of Geology: Issues 9-12 Cục địa chất Việt Nam - 1997 "2. 7. Cả River zone: This zone lies along the Cả River and Rào Nay basins, with a length of 300 km"</ref> 

在接近河口的[[榮市|榮市]]邊水，建有邊水橋以跨越藍江。

